Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.81,main,,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to rest or \Nsleep until we make up!}Cho đến khi tụi anh làm lành,\N  anh sẽ không nghỉ hay ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.73,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Please don't put yourself in danger!}Xin đừng cố quá nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:36.78,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Saki-chan must be worried about \Nmy relationship with two girls.}Chắc saki-chan đang lo về việc bắt cá hai tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.11,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Are you really...}anh thật sự....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:41.06,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I want to put her at ease as soon as I can.}Anh muốn làm em ấy an tâm hơn nhanh nhất có thể
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:44.95,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I'm going to stay up all night \Nto write a love letter to her!}Anh sẽ thức trắng đêm để viết thư tình cho em ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:50.66,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Could I at least make you a nutritious meal?}Ít nhật thì hãy để em nấu cho anh bữa ăn đầy dinh dưỡng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.15,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.59,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Let me talk to you, please!}Hãy nói chuyện với anh đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.04,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.05,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Shut up! Don't talk to me!}Ồn ào quá! đừng nói chuyện với em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:03.97,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Then read this letter I wrote for you!}Vậy thì hãy đọc lá thư này của anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.41,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{So heavy!}Nặng dữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.69,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I'm not reading that!}Em không đọc đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.11,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Fine...}được thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.04,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{"My Feelings for Saki-chan: Chapter One!}Tình cảm của anh dành cho Saki-chan: Chương 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:15.96,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{My love is..."}Tình cảm của tôi là..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.77,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Don't read it out loud!}Đừng có đọc nó lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.12,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Naoya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.94,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I'm not done yet.}Chưa xong đâu.
