Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:16.33,top,Naoya,0,0,0,,What's your favorite season? Summer? Winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:17.26,top,Saki,0,0,0,,Summer, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:18.46,top,Saki,0,0,0,,Because there's summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.46,0:24:20.80,top,Nagisa,0,0,0,,It's not one of the two choices,\Nbut I'd say spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:23.20,top,Nagisa,0,0,0,,That was the season when I met Naoya-kun.
